M	src/sieve-tools/sievec.c
M	src/testsuite/testsuite.c

2012-08-12 16:16:21 +0200 Stephan Bosch <stephan@rename-it.nl> (4dcfc2d)

    lib-sieve: Adjusted edit-mail.c to changes in Dovecot mail storage API.


